    </para>
    <para id="id9261478">3/ Isolation</para>
    <para id="id9261485">With the use of an op-amp, the two systems can be isolated from each other or buffered so that the system function is the product of the individual system functions.</para>
    <para id="id9261504">
      <media id="id1170067785526" alt=""><image src="../../media/graphics5-633d.png" mime-type="image/png" height="160" width="439"/></media>
    </para>
