    <para id="id9231356">Two-minute miniquiz problem</para>
    <para id="id9231360">Problem 8-1 Simple position control system</para>
    <para id="id9231364">The objective of the position control system shown below is for the output position Y (s) to track the input signal X(s).</para>
    <figure id="id9487334">
      <media id="id1170064766266" alt=""><image src="../../media/graphics12-7358.png" mime-type="image/png" height="116" width="475"/></media>
    </figure>
    <para id="id9487358">a) Determine the closed-loop system function H(s) = Y (s)/X(s).</para>
    <para id="id9487416">b) For x(t) = u(t), a unit step, determine the steady state value of y(t).</para>
    <para id="id9487474">Solution</para>
    <list id="id9487479" list-type="enumerated">
      <item>We can use Black’s formula to find H(s) as follows</item>
    </list>
    <para id="id9487508">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mstyle fontsize="12pt">
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>H</m:mi>
                  <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                      <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                      <m:mfrac>
                        <m:mfrac>
                          <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                            <m:mrow>
                              <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                            </m:mrow>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                            <m:mrow>
                              <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                              <m:mtext>100</m:mtext>
                            </m:mrow>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                          </m:mrow>
                        </m:mfrac>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                          <m:mfrac>
                            <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                            <m:mrow>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                              <m:mrow>
                                <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                                <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                                <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                              </m:mrow>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                              <m:mrow>
                                <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                                <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                                <m:mtext>100</m:mtext>
                              </m:mrow>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                            </m:mrow>
                          </m:mfrac>
                        </m:mrow>
                      </m:mfrac>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                    <m:mfrac>
                      <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                        </m:mrow>
                        <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                        <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                          <m:mtext>100</m:mtext>
                        </m:mrow>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
