    <para id="id7133074">4/ Improve dynamic characteristics</para>
    <para id="id7133082">Our model of an op-amp was simplistic. A more realistic model that takes the finite bandwidth of the op-amp into account is shown below.</para>
    <figure id="id7133091">
      <media id="id1170065764310" alt=""><image src="../../media/graphics17-c906.png" mime-type="image/png" height="157" width="518"/></media>
    </figure>
    <para id="id7133115">The finite bandwidth of the op-amp is modeled as</para>
    <para id="id7133120">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mstyle fontsize="12pt">
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                  <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                    <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                    <m:mfrac>
                      <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                        <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                        <m:mi>α</m:mi>
                      </m:mrow>
                    </m:mfrac>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mstyle>
            <m:mrow/>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{K \( s \) = {  {K}  over  {s+α} } } {}</m:annotation>
        </m:semantics>
      </m:math>
    </para>
    <para id="id7133196">Using Black’s formula we obtain</para>
    <para id="id7133201">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mstyle fontsize="12pt">
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>H</m:mi>
                  <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                        <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                        <m:mfrac>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                            <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                          </m:mrow>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mrow>
                              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                              <m:mi fontstyle="italic">βK</m:mi>
                            </m:mrow>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                            <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                          </m:mrow>
                        </m:mfrac>
                      </m:mrow>
                      <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                      <m:mfrac>
                        <m:mfrac>
                          <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                            <m:mi>α</m:mi>
                          </m:mrow>
                        </m:mfrac>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                            <m:mi>β</m:mi>
                          </m:mrow>
                          <m:mfrac>
                            <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                            <m:mrow>
                              <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                              <m:mi>α</m:mi>
                            </m:mrow>
                          </m:mfrac>
                        </m:mrow>
                      </m:mfrac>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                    <m:mfrac>
                      <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mi>s</m:mi>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                        </m:mrow>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mi>α</m:mi>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                          <m:mi fontstyle="italic">βK</m:mi>
                        </m:mrow>
                        <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                      </m:mrow>
                    </m:mfrac>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mstyle>
            <m:mrow/>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{H \( s \) = {  {K \( s \) }  over  {1+βK \( s \) } } = {  { {  {K}  over  {s+α} } }  over  {1+β {  {K}  over  {s+α} } } } = {  {K}  over  {s+ \( α+βK \) } } } {}</m:annotation>
        </m:semantics>
      </m:math>
    </para>
    <para id="id7133390">Therefore, the frequency response is</para>
    <para id="id7133394">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mstyle fontsize="12pt">
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>H</m:mi>
                  <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi fontstyle="italic">jω</m:mi>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                    <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                    <m:mfrac>
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mi>K</m:mi>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">/</m:mo>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                        </m:mrow>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mi>α</m:mi>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                          <m:mi fontstyle="italic">βK</m:mi>
                        </m:mrow>
                        <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                      </m:mrow>
                      <m:mrow>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mi fontstyle="italic">jω</m:mi>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">/</m:mo>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo>
                        </m:mrow>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mi>α</m:mi>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                          <m:mi fontstyle="italic">βK</m:mi>
                        </m:mrow>
                        <m:mrow>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo>
                          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                        </m:mrow>
                      </m:mrow>
                    </m:mfrac>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mstyle>
            <m:mrow/>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{H \( jω \) = {  {K/ \( α+βK \) }  over  {jω/ \( α+βK \) +1} } } {}</m:annotation>
        </m:semantics>
      </m:math>
    </para>
    <para id="id8600212">the impulse response is</para>
    <para id="id8600217">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mstyle fontsize="12pt">
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>h</m:mi>
