        </m:semantics>
      </m:math>
    </para>
    <para id="id8002122">How good is this system at controlling the motor position?</para>
    <para id="id8002127">Let us examine the steady-state step response first. The system function is</para>
    <para id="id8002133">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mstyle fontsize="12pt">
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
