    <para id="id9343887">where α &gt; 0 and β &gt; 0. These conditions are both necessary and sufficient.</para>
    <para id="id9343913">2/ Third-order polynomials</para>
    <para id="id9343917">Third-order polynomials must have one real root and either a pair of real or complex roots of the form</para>
