    <para id="id7833600">Note that α &gt; 0, β &gt; 0, and γ &gt; 0. But in addition, β &gt; γ/α. These conditions are both necessary and sufficient.</para>
    <para id="id9143095">VI. ROOT LOCUS PLOTS FOR POSITION CONTROL SYSTEMS</para>
